about1: This questionnaire contains 20 pairs of statements which give different views on certain things. Using a five-point rating scale, circle the number that most closely reflects your view according to the following:
about2: (2) Strongly agree with the statement on the left.
about2_1: (1) Agree with the statement on the left.
about2_3: (-1) Agree with the statement on the right.
about2_4: (-2) Strongly agree with the statement on the right.
